	<h3 id="interests"><u>My Interests</u></h3>
	<p>What inspired me to do a joint honours degree with computing, is that I was facinated by the great advances and rapid development of technology; its impact it has on our postmodern society. I sought this degree as an opportunity for me to engage in this technological movement.
      So far on my course, I have learned how to program in Java, HTML and how to use command line. I believe that with the skills I have aquired so far will enable me to progress in my studies; help me earn internship placements this coming summer.
      My ambition is to improve my technological skills - in that case master programming languages such as: HTML, Java, Javascript and PHP. I know that by mastering these programming languages I will be able to improve my technological skills and problem solving skills.</p>
